        "scraping_time": "2025-03-15T13.00.04",
        "en_title": "MELONI SENTE STARMER, ANCHE LEI IN CALL Commitment for peace and security in Ukraine But it is not expected to send troops",
        "en_content": "Meloni: commitment to peace, no sending troops The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, telephoned the British Premier Starmer. The premier participated in the Call with London linking several international leaders of the \"coalition of the voluntarians\". The coalition is committed to securing the security of Kiev in the Moscow war. Meloni reiterated that Italy intends to continue working with European partners and the United States for peace and security in Ukraine, but does not plan to send troops on the ground.",
