        "en_title": "STARMER TO \"VOLENTEROSI\":BASTA WITH PUTIN \"No his games on truce Trump\"",
        "en_content": "Starmer to \"volenterosis\":basta with Putin British Prime Minister Keir Starmer issued a message on X before the video conference with leaders from 25 countries of the so-called \"Coalition of Anglo-French-led voluntarists\" committed to guarantee security in Kiev even after possible peace with Russia. Among the countries of the coalition as well as Europeans Australia and New Zealand. \"We cannot allow President Putin to play games on the agreement presented by President Trump.\"And in the Call:\"Putin sooner or later will have to sit at the Peace Table\". \"Prepare to defend a peace agreement.\"",
